The 1st layer of the OSI model is the Physical layer; a mnemonic to help remember this is 'Please Do Not Throw Sausage Pizza Away', where: 
	1.) 'Please' -> Physical;
	2.) 'Do' -> Data Link;
	3.) 'Not' -> Network;
	4.) 'Throw' -> Transport;
	5.) 'Sausage' -> Session;
	6.) 'Pizza' -> Presentation;
	7.) 'Away' -> Application.

